---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us - 1099TaxEst">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">About 1099TaxEst</h1>
		<div class="fintech-card p-8 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
			<p>1099TaxEst was built to help freelancers, independent contractors, and small business owners quickly estimate their federal tax burden.</p>
			<p>Taxes can be complicated, and many online calculators ask for too much personal information. We built a tool that calculates your estimated tax burden completely in your browser. We don't store your financial data, we don't ask for your email, and we don't send anything to a server.</p>
			<p>Our goal is to help you set aside the right amount of money for tax season so you're never caught off guard.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
